window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>\"Honor the Code and you'll rest in your next life!\" they said . . . </p> <p>\"It'll be fun!\" they said . . . </p> <p>Now why didn't <i>they</i> tell me I'd have to get married and be responsible for a whole Noble Family of my own, with a bunch of obligations and all the crap I have to deal with now!? Could I get reborn back into a Hunter again, please!?</p>"; 
